      <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="hover:underline">$ cat rss.xml</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/marketmax" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">$ cat twitter</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ketanjawale" class="hover:underline">$ cat linkedin</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</footer>
<div class="container-blog pb-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-text-muted">
